description:
David ran to defeat Goliath with a sling and five stones, but he wasnt trusting those things to bring victory. He trusted God  trusted Him enough that he ran, alone, toward a giant and an army. If you know you are doing Gods will you just need to go forward trusting God.

"The Shepherd King" is a 12-part revival series with Pastor @PastorBatchelorfirst aired in Spring of 2017.
